= SDL_RenderFillRect =
Use this function to fill a rectangle on the current rendering target with the drawing color.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_RenderFillRect(const SDL_Rect* rect)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''rect'''
|a pointer to the destination rectangle, or NULL for the entire rendering target
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or -1 if there is no rendering context current; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

